OL,3,CMan in court after police officer
OL,4,Cstabbed in neck and dog attacked
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court to face
OL,7,Fmultiple charges after a female police
OL,8,Fofficer was stabbed in the neck.
OL,10,F25-year-old Soul Henry appeared at
OL,11,FKidderminster Magistrates' court
OL,12,Fearlier today facing multiple charges
OL,13,Fincluding attempted murder and
OL,14,Fcriminal damage in relation to a
OL,15,Fpolice dog.
OL,17,FThe charges relate to an incident on
OL,18,FSunday night in which a female police
OL,19,Fofficer was stabbed in the village of
OL,20,FClifton in Worcestershire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
