OL,3,CMan in court after police officer
OL,4,Cstabbed in neck and dog attacked
OL,6,FIt was a brief hearing this lunchtime
OL,7,Flasting around 5 minutes.
OL,9,FThe 25-year-old, of no fixed address,
OL,10,Fappeared from police custody wearing a
OL,11,Fgrey tracksuit, with a tattoo on his
OL,12,Fneck.
OL,14,FHenry is also charged with burglary
OL,15,Fand possession of a bladed article.
OL,17,FHe did not enter a plea. He spoke to
OL,18,Fconfirm his name and date of birth.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
