OL,3,CMan in court after police officer
OL,4,Cstabbed in neck and dog attacked
OL,6,FIn court today the magistrates said
OL,7,Fthey have to send his case to crown
OL,8,Fcourt because of the charge of
OL,9,Fattempted murder.
OL,11,FHenry was was remanded in custody and
OL,12,Fis due to appear at Worcester Crown
OL,13,FCourt on the 20th May for a trial and
OL,14,Fpreparation hearing.
